<h2>How Google Algorithm Updates Work</h2>
<p>Google uses hundreds of ranking factors processed through multiple systems. An "algorithm update" is a change to one or more of those systems. Some changes are small. Others rewrite how Google evaluates entire categories of content.</p>
<h3>Types of Google Updates</h3>
